room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Tri-State Escape in Huntington
review: My family had a blast. We did the jail break room it was hard but so much fun. The staff was very friendly and accommodating. Defiantly be coming back!

room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Tri-State Escape in Huntington
review: Had such a great time. Went with a group of eight with ages 5, teenagers and 30 some year olds. We did jail break. Everyone had a blast. I'm always trying to find something fun to do with the family and this was perfect. It was well worth the money! Will do it again for sure. Staff was great as well!
